  <article id="instructions">
    We are a used book store, which means books come and go and we don't have a
    regulated stock of books. If you would like to find out if we have a
    specific book on hand, please fill out this form. If we have a copy, we'll
    contact you, then pull it and hold it for 24 hours for you to pick up or get
    back to us with a later time you can pick it up. If we don't have a copy,
    we'll still contact you.
  </article>

